Interface FieldModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<FieldId,java.lang.Object>>, StringMapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractWrapper, BaseFieldModel, GenericModel, ModelInterceptor, RuntimeModel

    public interface FieldModel
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<FieldId,java.lang.Object>>, StringMapper
    An model that maps FieldId to values. Each FieldId can map to at most one value.
